@startuml
' Sequence diagram: interaksi LINTAS-LAPIS Elixir <-> Kubernetes (PDB sadar-kuorum).
' Bagian atas = loop reconcile operator; bagian bawah = gangguan sukarela (drain) ditolak PDB.
' Tema PlantUML/UML standar. Render: plantuml -tpdf seq_crosslayer.puml
title Interaksi lintas-lapis Elixir <-> Kubernetes (PDB sadar-kuorum)

actor "Admin\n(kubectl drain)" as Adm
participant "PDBOperator\n(Elixir + kubectl)" as Op
participant "API server /\nPodDisruptionBudget" as API
participant "Pod aplikasi\n(QuorumProbe, ProbeHTTP)" as Pod

== Loop reconcile operator (tiap 5 detik) ==
Op -> API : kubectl get pods
API --> Op : daftar IP pod
Op -> Pod : HTTP GET /probe
Pod --> Op : {n, q (ambang kuorum)}
Op -> Op : Quorum.budget(...)  ->  minAvailable = Q
Op -> API : kubectl patch pdb\nminAvailable = Q

== Gangguan sukarela (drain / rolling update) ==
Adm -> API : minta usir (evict) pod
alt eviction akan memecah kuorum (available - 1 < Q)
  API --> Adm : DENY (HTTP 429, dijaga PDB)
  note over Adm #ccffcc: kuorum BEAM terjaga
else masih dalam budget (available - 1 >= Q)
  API --> Adm : ALLOW (pod keluar)
end
@enduml
